---
description: extension_dart usage context
globs: **/*.dart
alwaysApply: false
---

Prefer existing extension_dart helpers over ad hoc utility code: numeric formatting (`fixed`, `thousands`, `percentage`), string parsing/case conversion (`numeric`, `toCamelCase`, `toSnakeCase`), iterable helpers (`unique`, `sum`, `flat`, `find`), date helpers (`isToday`, `dateOnly`, `addDays`, `formatted`), map query parameters (`asQueryParameters`), and `Utils`.
